	<description>
	Highscore is an arcade game set in arcades houses the years 80/90, the player takes part in a top competition highscorer where those who have their name on the maximum number of machines wins.
	</description>
	
	<history>
	    An arcade house called "Arcade" is every year a big competition where all machines are free so that competitors try to achieve the maximum highscores of the machines.
        A child known as AAA was several times winner of the competition, leaving your name in most games, preventing its competitors beat your score. 
        Until one day she vanished, along with most of the arcade houses... 
        After years of arcade Arcade house reopened, and a new competition began. 
	</history>

